= redmine_google_links

DESCRIPTION

This plugins adds two macros ('gmail' and 'gdoc') to your Redmine Wiki.


USAGE EXAMPLES

{{gmail("Mike's Dirthday")}} will insert a link to GMail search results page for "Mike's Birthday" query string. 

Similar, type {{idoc("Budget")}} to insert a link to a Google Docs named "Budget".


INSTALLATION

Put 'redmine_google_links' directory under your vendor/plugins directory. No need to run db:migrate_plugins script.

cd <redmine>/vendor/plugins
git clone http://github.com/vovayartsev/redmine_google_links.git


BUGS & IMPROVEMENTS

Found a bug? Create a ticket here: http://github.com/vovayartsev/redmine_google_links/issues


